Class SystemDefaultValue

All Implemented Interfaces:
CSSPrimitiveValue, CSSTypedValue, CSSValue, Serializable, Cloneable
public class SystemDefaultValue
extends TypedValue
When a system-dependent property must be set but there is no style database, this value can be used.
